'''天鵝座X-1'''（簡稱'''Cyg X-1'''）<ref name=science3656/>是一個银河系内位于[[天鵝座|天鵝座]]的双星系统，是著名的[[X射線源|X射線源]]。<ref>{{cite news
 | author=Staff
 | date=2004-11-05
 | publisher=ESA
 | title=Observations: Seeing in X-ray wavelengths
 | url=http://www.esa.int/esaSC/SEMTA2T1VED_index_0.html
 | accessdate=2008-08-12
 | archive-date=2008-10-11
 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081011192014/http://www.esa.int/esaSC/SEMTA2T1VED_index_0.html
 | dead-url=no
 }}</ref>它在1964年的一次[[火箭|火箭]]彈道飛行時被發現，是從地球觀測最強的X射綫源之一，其頂峰X射綫[[通量|通量]]為2.3{{e|−23}} [[瓦特|W]][[公分|m]]<sup>−2</sup>[[赫茲|Hz]]<sup>−1</sup><ref>{{cite book
 | first=Walter | last=Lewin
 | coauthors=Van Der Klis, Michiel | year=2006
 | title=Compact Stellar X-ray Sources
 | publisher=Cambridge University Press
 | pages=159 | isbn=0521826594 }}</ref><ref>The following source:
:{{cite web
 | title=2010 X-Ray Sources
 | publisher=U.S. Naval Observatory
 | work=The Astronomical Almanac
 | url=http://asa.usno.navy.mil/SecH/Xray.html
 | accessdate=2009-08-04
 | archive-date=2010-03-28
 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100328235619/http://asa.usno.navy.mil/SecH/Xray.html
 | dead-url=yes
 }}
gives a range of {{nowrap|235–1320 μJy}} at energies of {{nowrap|2–10 kEv}}.</ref>。天鵝座X-1是最先被廣泛承認為[[黑洞|黑洞]]的候選[[星體|星體]]，也是同類星體中最受研究關注的。現在估計其質量為[[太陽質量|太陽質量]]的14.8倍，<ref name=iorio/>而其密度之高使黑洞成爲唯一一種解釋。如果如此，它的[[事件視界|事件視界]]半徑約為26公里。<ref>{{cite web | last=Harko | first=T. | date=June 28, 2006 | url=http://www.physics.hku.hk/~astro/harko_science.html | title=Black Holes | publisher=University of Hong Kong | accessdate=2008-03-28 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090210234214/http://www.physics.hku.hk/~astro/harko_science.html | archivedate=2009-02-10 }}</ref>

天鵝座X-1屬於一個[[X射線雙星#高質量X射線雙星|高質量X射線雙星]]系統，其距離[[太陽|太陽]]大約6,070[[光年|光年]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://pansci.tw/archives/9489 |title=天文學家完成黑洞三根毛理論完整敘述 |accessdate=2011-11-28 |archive-date=2011-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111128193242/http://pansci.tw/archives/9489 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，另一成員為一顆[[超巨星|超巨星]][[變星|變星]]，編號為HDE 226868。兩者相互圍繞公轉，距離為0.2天文單位，即地球和太陽間距離的20%。該星的[[星風|星風]]為X射綫源的[[吸積盤|吸積盤]]提供物質。<ref name=apj304/>盤的内部溫度達到幾百萬[[開氏度|K]]，因此輻射出X射綫。<ref>{{cite web | last=Nayakshin | first=Sergei | coauthors=James B. Dove | date=November 3, 1998 | url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1998astro.ph.11059N | title=X-rays From Magnetic Flares In Cygnus X-1: The Role Of A Transition Layer | publisher=Cornell University | accessdate=2008-03-29 | archive-date=2012-03-27 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66Sy5SRNr?url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1998astro.ph.11059N | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=mnras325/>兩條垂直于吸積盤的[[相對論性噴流|相對論性噴流]]將被吸進的物質噴射出星際空間。<ref>{{cite journal | last=Gallo | first=Elena | coauthors=Fender, Rob | title=Accretion modes and jet production in black hole X-ray binaries | journal=Memorie della Società Astronomica Italiana | year=2005 | volume=75 | pages=282–290 | url=http://arxiv.org/abs/astro-ph?papernum=0509172 | accessdate=2008-03-29 | archive-date=2022-02-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220212000904/https://arxiv.org/abs/astro-ph?papernum=0509172 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

這個系統可能屬於一個名為天鵝座OB3的[[星協|星協]]，意味著天鵝座X-1的年齡超過500萬年，並源于一顆質量大於40個太陽質量的原星。這顆原星的大部分質量都散失了，很可能是以星風的形式。如果該星以[[超新星|超新星]]的形式爆炸，則其威力足以將剩餘物質噴射出這個系統。因此它可能直接坍縮成一個黑洞。<ref name=science300/>

[[物理學家|物理學家]][[史蒂芬·霍金|史蒂芬·霍金]]和[[基普·索恩|基普·索恩]]曾拿天鵝座X-1作了一場科學的賭局。當中霍金賭天鵝座X-1不是一顆黑洞。1990年霍金讓步，因爲觀測證據顯示這個系統中存在著[[引力奇點|引力奇點]]。<ref>{{cite news
 | author=Staff
 | date=February 27, 2004
 | title=Galaxy Entree or Main Course?
 | publisher=Swinburne University
 | url=http://astronomy.swin.edu.au/sao/astronomynews/astronews2004s1.xml
 | accessdate=2008-03-31
 | archive-date=2008-05-02
 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080502042527/http://astronomy.swin.edu.au/sao/astronomynews/astronews2004s1.xml
 | dead-url=no
 }}</ref>

==發現及觀測==
通過對X射線源的觀測，[[天文學家|天文學家]]能研究涉及到幾百萬度熾熱氣體的天文現象。但由於X射線被地球的[[大氣層|大氣層]]遮擋了，因此[[X射線天文學|對X射線源的觀測]]不能在地表進行，而需要將儀器運送到有足夠X射線能穿透的高度。<ref>{{cite book
 | first=Friedman | last=Herbert | year=2002
 | chapter=From the ionosphere to high energy astronomy – a personal experience
 | title=The Century of Space Science
 | publisher=Springer | isbn=0792371968 }}</ref><ref name=apj611/>發現天鵝座X-1的儀器是從[[新墨西哥州|新墨西哥州]][[白沙導彈靶場|白沙導彈靶場]]由火箭發射到彈道軌道。1964年時正進行一項觀測，目的是找出這些X射線源。兩個空蜂火箭（Aerobee）彈道火箭運載著[[蓋革計數器|蓋革計數器]]升空，測量天空中8.4°範圍内[[波長|波長]]從1至15[[埃|Å]]的X射線源。<ref name=science3656/>

這項觀測發現了8個新的X射線源，包括天鵝座的Cyg XR-1（後名Cyg X-1）。其[[天球坐標|天球坐標]]估計為[[赤經|赤經]]19<sup>h</sup>53<sup>m</sup>、[[赤緯|赤緯]]34.6°。該X射線源處並沒有明顯的[[無線電天文學|無線電]]或[[可見光|可見光]]源。<ref name=science3656>{{cite journal | last=Bowyer | first=S. | coauthors=Byram, E. T.; Chubb, T. A.; Friedman, H. | title=Cosmic X-ray Sources | journal=Science | year=1965 | volume=147 | issue=3656 | pages=394–398 | url=http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/abstract/147/3656/394 | accessdate=2008-03-10 | doi=10.1126/science.147.3656.394 | pmid=17832788 | archive-date=2009-02-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090210142913/http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/abstract/147/3656/394 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

由於需要更長時間的觀測研究，1963年[[里卡尔多·贾科尼|里卡尔多·贾科尼]]和[[赫伯特·格斯基|赫伯特·格斯基]]提出了首個研究X射線源的軌道衛星。[[美國太空總署|美國太空總署]]於1970年發射了[[乌呼鲁卫星|乌呼鲁卫星]]，<ref>{{cite web | author=Staff | date=June 26, 2003 | url=http://heasarc.gsfc.nasa.gov/docs/uhuru/uhuru.html | title=The Uhuru Satellite | publisher=NASA | accessdate=2008-05-09 | archive-date=2008-05-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080514202753/http://heasarc.gsfc.nasa.gov/docs/uhuru/uhuru.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>進而發現了300個新X射線源。<ref>{{cite web
 | last=Giacconi
 | first=Riccardo
 | date=December 8, 2002
 | url=http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/physics/laureates/2002/giacconi-lecture.html
 | title=The Dawn of X-Ray Astronomy
 | publisher=The Nobel Foundation
 | accessdate=2008-03-24
 | archive-date=2008-04-29
 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080429224744/http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/physics/laureates/2002/giacconi-lecture.html
 | dead-url=no
 }}</ref>它對天鵝座X-1的長期觀測發現其X光強度有波動，頻率為每秒數次。<ref>{{cite journal
 | last=Oda
 | first=M.
 | coauthors=Gorenstein, P.; Gursky, H.; Kellogg, E.; Schreier, E.; Tananbaum, H.; Giacconi, R.
 | title=X-Ray Pulsations from Cygnus X-1 Observed from UHURU
 | journal=The Astrophysical Journal
 | year=1999
 | volume=166
 | pages=L1–L7
 | url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1971ApJ...166L...1O
 | accessdate=2008-03-11
 | doi=10.1086/180726
 | archive-date=2008-01-21
 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080121173017/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1971ApJ...166L...1O
 | dead-url=no
 }}</ref>如此快速的變動顯示，能量一定在很小的範圍内產生，大小約為10<sup>5</sup>公里<ref>這相當於光在三分之一秒内所走的距離。</ref>，因爲[[光速|光速]]的限制使訊息不可能在更遠的範圍裏相互傳遞。作爲對比，[[太陽|太陽]]的直徑約為1.4{{e|6}}公里。

1971年4月至5月，[[萊登天文臺|萊登天文臺]]的Luc Braes和George Miley與[[美國國家射電天文臺|美國國家射電天文臺]]的Robert M. Hjellming和Campbell Wade<ref>{{cite journal
 | last=Kristian | first=J. | coauthors=Brucato, R.; Visvanathan, N.; Lanning, H.; Sandage, A.
 | title=On the Optical Identification of Cygnus X-1
 | url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1971ApJ...168L..91K
 | journal=The Astrophysical Journal
 | year=1971 | volume=168 | pages=L91–L93 | accessdate=2008-03-10
 | doi=10.1086/180790 }}</ref>獨立探測到來自天鵝座X-1的無線電射線，射線源的準確位置指向AGK2 +35 1910 = HDE 226868。<ref>{{cite journal
 | last=Braes | first=L.L.E. | coauthors=Miley, G.K.| date=July 23, 1971
 | title=Physical Sciences: Detection of Radio Emission from Cygnus X-1
 | url=https://archive.org/details/sim_nature-uk_1971-07-23_232_5308/page/246 | journal=Nature 
 | volume=232 | pages=246
 | doi=10.1038/232246a0 | bibcode=1971Natur.232Q.246B
 | pmid=16062947
 | issue=5308}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal
 | last=Braes | first=L.L.E. | coauthors=Miley, G.K.
 | year=1971
 | title=Variable Radio Emission from X-Ray Sources
 | journal=Veröffentlichungen Remeis-Sternwarte Bamberg
 | volume=9 | issue=100 | pages=173
 | publisher=(IAU Colloquium No.15, Bamberg, Germany, August 31-September 3, 1971. Bibcode: 1972VeBam.100......)}}</ref>
[[天球|天球]]上，這顆星與[[視星等|視星等]]為4級的[[天鵝座η|天鵝座η]]相距半度。<ref name=bernard>{{cite book
 | first=Bernard | last=Abrams | coauthors=Stecker, Michael
 | title=Structures in Space: Hidden Secrets of the Deep Sky
 | year=1999 | pages=91 | publisher=Springer
 | isbn=1852331658 |quote=Eta Cygni is 25 arc minutes to the west-south-west of this star.}}</ref>它是一顆[[超巨星|超巨星]]，本身並不能發射所觀測到的X射線。因此，此星必定有一顆能够將氣體加熱到幾百萬度的伴星，才可放射在天鵝座X-1觀測到的輻射。

[[皇家格林威治天文台|皇家格林威治天文台]]的Louise Webster和Paul Murdin與<ref>{{cite journal | last=Webster | first=B. Louise | coauthors=Murdin, Paul | title=Cygnus X-1—a Spectroscopic Binary with a Heavy Companion? | journal=Nature | year=1972 | volume=235 | issue=2 | pages=37–38 | url=http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v235/n5332/abs/235037a0.html | accessdate=2008-03-10 | doi=10.1038/235037a0 | archive-date=2007-12-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071218202247/http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v235/n5332/abs/235037a0.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>單獨在[[多倫多大學|多倫多大學]][[大衛·鄧拉普天文台|大衛·鄧拉普天文台]]工作的 Charles Thomas Bolton<ref>{{cite journal | last=Bolton | first=C. T. | year=1972 | title=Identification of Cygnus X-1 with HDE 226868 | journal=Nature | volume=235 | issue=2 | pages=271–273 | url=http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v235/n5336/abs/235271b0.html | accessdate=2008-03-10 | doi=10.1038/235271b0 | archive-date=2016-11-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161114013605/http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v235/n5336/abs/235271b0.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>於1971年公佈了HDE 226868巨型伴星的發現消息。該星光譜的[[多普勒效應|多普勒效應]]顯示了其伴星的存在，人們也能根據軌道數據間接地測量其質量。<ref name=luminet>{{cite book
 | first=Jean-Pierre | last=Luminet | year=1992
 | title=Black Holes | url=https://archive.org/details/blackholes0000lumi | publisher=Cambridge University Press
 | isbn=0521409063 }}</ref>由於該天體質量很高，他們推測它可能是一個[[黑洞|黑洞]]。因為最大的[[中子星|中子星]]也不可能超過3個[[太陽質量|太陽質量]]。<ref>{{cite journal
 | last=Bombaci
 | first=I.
 | title=The maximum mass of a neutron star
 | journal=Astronomy and Astrophysics
 | year=1996
 | volume=305
 | pages=871–877
 | url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1996A&A...305..871B
 | accessdate=2008-03-11
 | doi=10.1088/1367-2630/7/1/199
 | archive-date=2019-03-30
 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330205633/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1996A%26A...305..871B
 | dead-url=no
 }}</ref>

隨著更多觀測證據的發現，到了1973年末，天文學界的普遍結論為天鵝座X-1最大可能為一黑洞。<ref>{{cite web | last=Rolston | first=Bruce | date=November 10, 1997 | url=http://news.utoronto.ca/bin/bulletin/nov10_97/art4.htm | title=The First Black Hole | publisher=University of Toronto | accessdate=2008-03-11 | archive-date=2008-03-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080307181205/http://www.news.utoronto.ca/bin/bulletin/nov10_97/art4.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last=Shipman | first=H. L. | title=The implausible history of triple star models for Cygnus X-1 Evidence for a black hole | journal=Astrophysical Letters | year=1975 | volume=16 | issue=1 | pages=9–12 | url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1975ApL....16....9S | accessdate=2008-03-11 | archive-date=2018-10-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181005101528/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1975ApL....16....9S | dead-url=no }}</ref>對天鵝座X-1更精確的測量顯示出小至1毫秒的變化。這個間距與黑洞[[吸積盤|吸積盤]]物質的亂流相符。持續三分之一秒的X射線爆符合物質掉進黑洞預測所需的時間。<ref name=apj189>{{cite journal
